npm start //to start 

git commands
============
git init
git clone https://github.com/swethanaidu/ppqas.git //project clone in local
git pull origin main //to pull updated code & main is out master branch 
git branch branch1 // to create branch
git add . // to add all files
git add file_name // to add particular file to stage
git commit -m "first commit" // add commit 
git push origin main // to push code to main
